      "description": "Project-grade example being offered honestly as a poor-condition car. Expect significant cosmetic wear, tired paint, an aged interior, and the likelihood of deferred maintenance throughout. This is not a turn-key driver and should be approached as a restoration project, repair candidate, or possible parts car depending on the buyer\u2019s goals. Best suited for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at and is prepared for substantial work.",
