      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly project car with plenty of room for the next owner to bring it back. This one is in poor overall condition and shows significant wear, so it\u2019s best suited for someone looking for a fixer-upper, parts car, or restoration candidate. Honest value here for a buyer who knows what they\u2019re getting and wants an affordable entry point.",
