    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values practicality, affordability, and the opportunity to put their own touch on it. A straightforward option for commuting, errands, or a starter project, priced to reflect strong value.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels that gets the job done? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transportation, a project, or a handy spare runaround. It\u2019s priced with its age and wear in mind, and for the right buyer it could be a great little opportunity without spending a fortune. If you want something affordable and straightforward, come take a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project opportunity with the kind of mechanical foundation enthusiasts look for. The engine fires up and the drivetrain feels like it still has plenty of life left, with steering, braking, and suspension offering a workable base for someone who knows their way around a toolbox. Cosmetic wear, age-related flaws, and general roughness are present, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. Great candidate for a budget build, parts donor, or dependable beater with some attention. If you want an affordable entry point with real upside, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap entry car. Rough around the edges, priced to sell fast.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true underdog with plenty of character, this car has the kind of honest, road-worn presence that turns errands into stories. It\u2019s the perfect canvas for a hands-on owner, weekend tinkerer, or anyone looking for budget-friendly wheels with soul. Distinctive, scrappy, and full of potential, this is the kind of ride that invites a little vision and rewards it with charm you just can\u2019t fake.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers a practical opportunity for a buyer who wants dependable basic transportation at an approachable cost. It shows wear consistent with its age and use, but it still presents solid value for someone seeking an inexpensive daily driver, project, or backup vehicle. Straightforward, honest, and affordably positioned, this is a chance to get behind the wheel without overspending.",
      "price": 5950.0,
